Package: togolab
Title: Shared Utilities for the Togo Lab
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ye Ji", "Choi", email = "yejichoi@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Togo Lab", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Lab-wide helper functions for the Bjornstad-Pyle-Tommerdahl (Togo)
    lab. Resolves per-user file system paths from an external
    configuration file, configures access to the lab S3 (Kopah) store, loads
    and collapses the harmonized dataset, and bundles miscellaneous utilities
    the lab uses across projects.
